    "body": "I can confirm that I've no issues after downgrading to Docker Compose 1.22.0 version.\r\n\r\nThis is my oneliner script to remove and reinstall Docker Compose version 1.22.0:\r\n\r\n```\r\nsudo \\rm -f /usr/local/bin/docker-compose && sudo curl -L \"https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.22.0/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)\" -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose && sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose && docker-compose --version\r\n```",
